{"id": "jvz1705579008327", "title": "Menu Properties", "breadcrumbs": ["Constructing Components and Other Objects", "Application Shells", "Libraries of Runtime Objects", "Menu Objects", "Menu Properties"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvz1705579008327.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Menu Properties</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:  ProcScript for Menus  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:  ProcScript for Menus  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eoe1705578839705.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:  Dynamic Menu Items  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:  Dynamic Menu Items  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kdw1705579836661.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvz1705579008327.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvz1705579008327.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvz1705579008327.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5829092\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5829092\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jvz1705579008327.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jvz1705579008327.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jvz1705579008327.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uqu1665702873174\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Menu Properties\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__menu_properties_88482\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Menu properties enable you to control the appearance of menus using the font, colors, and images. They are applicable only for Windows applications and are defined by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">menu</span> logical in the [application] section of the application initialization file (<span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__p_d26555e1_d26556e1_d26557e1\">You can set the default colors to use for the background and text, as well as other colors to indicate which item is selected, or items that are disabled in the current context.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__p_d26558e1_d26559e1_d26560e1\">When a color property is not defined, the Windows default is used.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Menu properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">Property</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Font</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Font used for text in menus.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbw1665702850998.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbw1665702850998.html\" title=\"Name of a logical font to be used for menus, as specified in the initialization file. If not specified, the Windows system default font is used.\">Font</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1 uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2 uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n                     Color Properties \n                  </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Background color of drop-down menu and\n\t\t\t\t popup menus. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColorSelect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Background color of the selected menu\n\t\t\t\t item. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ovj1665702629207.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ovj1665702629207.html\" title=\"Background color of a tab, menu item, or panel button when it has been selected.\">Active Background Color (BackColorSelect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColorSidebar</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Background color of the sidebar in\n\t\t\t\t drop-down and popup menus. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oam1665702851070.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oam1665702851070.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the sidebar in a menu. Valid value is a web or system color name, or a hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). If not specified, the Windows system default is used.\">BackColorSidebar</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColorFill</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Style of the background color for the selected\n                     menu item: <code class=\"ph codeph\">flat</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">gradient</code>.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpd1665702587794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpd1665702587794.html\" title=\"Determines whether the background color is styled with a flat or gradient color.\">Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BorderColorSelect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Color of the border around a selected menu\n\t\t\t\t item. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vyb1665702851141.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vyb1665702851141.html\" title=\"Color of the border around a selected menu item or panel button. Valid value is a web or system color name, or a hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). If not specified, the Windows system default is used.\">BorderColorSelect</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ForeColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\"> Color of the text in menu items and\n\t\t\t\t separators in menus. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbp1665702587714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbp1665702587714.html\" title=\"Color to use as the foreground (usually the text color).\">Foreground Color (ForeColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ForeColorSelect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Color of the text when the menu item is\n\t\t\t\t selected. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yvx1665702629417.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yvx1665702629417.html\" title=\"Color of the label text when the widget, tab, or menu item is selected. If not specified, the Foreground Color is used.\">Active Foreground Color (ForecolorSelect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ForeColorDisabled</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"></code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Color of the text when the menu item is\n\t\t\t\t disabled.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mqi1665702851211.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mqi1665702851211.html\" title=\"Color of the text when a menu item is disabled. Valid value is a web or system color name, or a hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). If not specified, the Windows system default is used.\">ForeColorDisabled</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1 uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2 uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n                     Image Properties \n                  </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ImgSelect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Image displayed as the selected menu item.\n\t\t\t\t </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"daw1665702633024.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/daw1665702633024.html\" title=\"The image that is displayed when the button, tab, or menu item is selected.\">Active Image (ImgSelect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ImgSidebar</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"></code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Image displayed as the side bar of a\n\t\t\t\t drop-down or popup menu. Overrides the <span class=\"keyword\">BackColorSidebar</span> property. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qsr1665702851284.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qsr1665702851284.html\" title=\"Name of the image file or glyph to use as the background of the menu sidebar.\">ImgSidebar</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ImgSize</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__2\">Size used to display an image in front of\n\t\t\t\t the menu item. Uniface always reserves an area in front of a menu item for an image. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqu1665702873174__table_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pjz1665702630239.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pjz1665702630239.html\" title=\"Defines the size used to display an icon in widgets and menu items, when both an image and text are defined for the value. Valid values are IMG_SMALL (default), IMG_MEDIUM, IMG_LARGE, IMG_XLARGE, or IMG_NONE.\">Image Size (ImgSize)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__note_w3848ab1b5b9b7_w3849ab1b5b9_w3850ab1b5_w3851ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> Using the\n        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Menu</span> setting bypasses the Windows theme manager, so you need to\n      explicitly specify all the properties you want to control. For each color property that is not\n      defined in the property string, the system-defined color is used, which gives menus a flat\n      appearance. You can use the BackColorFill property\n      to set the default to a <code class=\"ph codeph\">gradient</code> fill.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__section_ahq_3y3_d1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1011668e425\">Example: Setting Menu Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example sets the font, foreground, background, and\n                selection colors for menus. (For readability, this example is formatted over several\n                lines.)</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__pre_p4v_ky3_d1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">menu=umenu(font=SansMedium;\n                backcolor=#fdfdfd;forecolor=black;forecolorselect=green;\n                backcolorselect=#c0ddfc;bordercolorselect=#3399ff)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__fig_q4v_ky3_d1c\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Result</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Result of menu proeprties\" class=\"image\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__image_r4v_ky3_d1c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/enhancedmenu1.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__topic_d18042e1_d18043e1_d18044e1_d18045e1_d18046e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1011668e449\">\n                       \n Highlighting a Selection\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__p_d26579e1_d26580e1_d26581e1\">You can use BackColorSelect to specify a color or ImgSelect to specify an image to highlight the item that has focus.</p>\n<div class=\"note tip note_tip\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__note_cpf_ty3_d1c\"><span class=\"note__title\">Tip:</span> When defining the appearance of menus, keep in\n                mind that colors have a performance advantage over images.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__p_d26588e1_d26589e1_d26590e1\">If you specify a small image, it is automatically stretched to fit the width of the menu. For example, the image <span class=\"ph filepath\">yellow.png</span> is very small:</p>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__p_d26591e1_d26592e1_d26593e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__fig_w3843ab1b5c13b9b1_w3844ab1b5c13b9_w3845ab1b5c13_w3846ab1b5_w3847ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Small yellow image for menu or tab\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/yellow.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">menu=umenu(font=SansMedium;imgselect=@yellow.png)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__p_d26594e1_d26595e1_d26596e1\">In the displayed menu, it is expanded.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__fig_d26597e1_d26598e1_d26599e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Menu with ImgSelect Property</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Menu with image as selection highlight\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/menuwithimgselect.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__topic_d18047e1_d18048e1_d18049e1_d18050e1_d18051e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1011668e498\">\n                       \n Menu Sidebar\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__p_d26606e1_d26607e1_d26608e1\">By default, menus in Windows have a sidebar to the left of the menu items (or to the right if the application is configure for a right-to-left locale). This space is reserved to display an image or checkmark associated with the menu item. A separate color or image can be defined or the sidebar.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__p_d26609e1_d26610e1_d26611e1\">You can use the BackColorSidebar to define an alternative color for this sidebar, or the ImgSidebar to specify an image.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">menu=umenu(font=SansMedium;imgsidebar=@bluevertical.png)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"uqu1665702873174__fig_d26612e1_d26613e1_d26614e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 3. </span>Menu with Images for Sidebar and Selection</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Menu with Images for Sidebar and Selection\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/menuwithimgsidebar.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mwc1665702671394.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Menu</a><p>Set the font, color, and image properties for menus.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5829092\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5829092\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Menu Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Menu Properties Menu properties enable you to control the appearance of menus using the font, colors, and images. They are applicable only for Windows applications and are defined by the menu logical in the [application] section of the application initialization file ( usys.ini ). You can set the default colors to use for the background and text, as well as other colors to indicate which item is selected, or items that are disabled in the current context. When a color property is not defined, the Windows default is used. Table 1. Menu properties Property Description Details Font Font used for text in menus. Font Color Properties BackColor Background color of drop-down menu and popup menus. Background Color (BackColor) BackColorSelect Background color of the selected menu item. Active Background Color (BackColorSelect) BackColorSidebar Background color of the sidebar in drop-down and popup menus. BackColorSidebar BackColorFill Style of the background color for the selected menu item: flat or gradient . Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill) BorderColorSelect Color of the border around a selected menu item. BorderColorSelect ForeColor Color of the text in menu items and separators in menus. Foreground Color (ForeColor) ForeColorSelect Color of the text when the menu item is selected. Active Foreground Color (ForecolorSelect) ForeColorDisabled Color of the text when the menu item is disabled. ForeColorDisabled Image Properties ImgSelect Image displayed as the selected menu item. Active Image (ImgSelect) ImgSidebar Image displayed as the side bar of a drop-down or popup menu. Overrides the BackColorSidebar property. ImgSidebar ImgSize Size used to display an image in front of the menu item. Uniface always reserves an area in front of a menu item for an image. Image Size (ImgSize) Important: Using the Menu setting bypasses the Windows theme manager, so you need to explicitly specify all the properties you want to control. For each color property that is not defined in the property string, the system-defined color is used, which gives menus a flat appearance. You can use the BackColorFill property to set the default to a gradient fill. Example: Setting Menu Properties The following example sets the font, foreground, background, and selection colors for menus. (For readability, this example is formatted over several lines.) menu=umenu(font=SansMedium; backcolor=#fdfdfd;forecolor=black;forecolorselect=green; backcolorselect=#c0ddfc;bordercolorselect=#3399ff) Copy Figure 1. Result Highlighting a Selection You can use BackColorSelect to specify a color or ImgSelect to specify an image to highlight the item that has focus. Tip: When defining the appearance of menus, keep in mind that colors have a performance advantage over images. If you specify a small image, it is automatically stretched to fit the width of the menu. For example, the image yellow.png is very small: menu=umenu(font=SansMedium;imgselect=@yellow.png) Copy In the displayed menu, it is expanded. Figure 2. Menu with ImgSelect Property Menu Sidebar By default, menus in Windows have a sidebar to the left of the menu items (or to the right if the application is configure for a right-to-left locale). This space is reserved to display an image or checkmark associated with the menu item. A separate color or image can be defined or the sidebar. You can use the BackColorSidebar to define an alternative color for this sidebar, or the ImgSidebar to specify an image. menu=umenu(font=SansMedium;imgsidebar=@bluevertical.png) Copy Figure 3. Menu with Images for Sidebar and Selection Related Links Menu Set the font, color, and image properties for menus. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}